              <span class="font-black text-gray-900">Mixo ($9/mo)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Niche sites launched</span>
              <span class="font-black text-teal-600">47 sites in 18 months</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Avg site build time</span>
              <span class="font-black text-teal-600">23 minutes</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Monthly revenue</span>
              <span class="font-black text-teal-600">$4,700 (affiliate)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Total invested</span>
              <span class="font-black text-gray-900">$162 (18 months)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-600">ROI</span>
              <span class="font-black text-green-600">2,902% return</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic">"Mixo lets me spin up niche sites fast. I can test a keyword, see if it ranks, build more if it works. 47 sites later, I'm making $4,700/month from side projects. Webflow would have taken 10x longer per site."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-teal-400 p-5">
          <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">üé® Designer Agency: Webflow Premium Brand</h4>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Platform</span>
              <span class="font-black text-gray-900">Webflow ($42/mo)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Before Webflow</span>
              <span class="font-black text-gray-900">Squarespace (felt template-y)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
