            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-teal-100 pb-2">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Client perception</span>
              <span class="font-black text-teal-600">Premium agency (vs boutique)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Annual revenue increase</span>
              <span class="font-black text-teal-600">+$127,000</span>
